  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Thursday. Today I learned that my bedroom is apparently a five-star hotel for every insect in the neighborhood.",
      "zh": "星期四。今天我學到一件事：原來我房間根本是附近所有昆蟲眼中的五星級飯店。"
    },
    {
      "en": "It started with one small ant walking across my desk like it owned the place.",
      "zh": "事情從一隻小螞蟻開始，牠大搖大擺地走過我的書桌，好像這裡是牠的地盤。"
    },
    {
      "en": "One ant is not a big deal. One ant becomes a problem when it brings its entire family, and possibly its whole army, behind it.",
      "zh": "一隻螞蟻不算什麼大事，但當牠把整個家族，甚至整支軍隊都帶過來的時候，就變成一個問題了。"
    },
    {
      "en": "By the afternoon, there was a thin line of ants marching from my window to a crumb I dropped last week and completely forgot about.",
      "zh": "到了下午，已經有一長排螞蟻從我的窗戶排隊行進到一個我上週掉在地上、完全忘記的餅乾屑那裡。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I like to imagine there is a tiny queen somewhere in the wall, ordering her tiny soldiers to find more of my snacks.",
      "zh": "我喜歡想像牆壁裡某處有一隻小小的蟻后，正在命令牠的小小士兵們去找出更多我的零食。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Then I found a spider in the corner of my closet, quietly building a web like it was decorating an apartment.",
      "zh": "接著我在衣櫃角落發現一隻蜘蛛，安靜地織著網，好像在裝潢自己的公寓一樣。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Spiders do not scare me too much, but I still screamed a little when it moved faster than I expected.",
      "zh": "蜘蛛不會讓我太害怕，但牠移動的速度超出我預期，我還是忍不住小聲尖叫了一下。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Next came a snail, somehow all the way inside my room, dragging its shell slowly across the windowsill.",
      "zh": "接著出現了一隻蝸牛，不知怎麼一路爬進我房間，慢慢拖著牠的殼爬過窗台。"
    },
    {
      "en": "How does a snail even get up to the second floor? That is a mystery I do not have time to solve today.",
      "zh": "一隻蝸牛到底是怎麼爬到二樓的？這是一個我今天沒空解開的謎團。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A ladybug landed on my notebook next, bright red with tiny black spots, looking far too cute to be part of this invasion.",
      "zh": "接著一隻瓢蟲降落在我的筆記本上，鮮紅色配上一點一點的小黑斑，看起來太可愛了，實在不像是這場入侵的一份子。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I let the ladybug stay. Everyone deserves at least one guest who is not causing chaos.",
      "zh": "我讓瓢蟲留下來了，畢竟大家都值得至少有一位不會製造混亂的客人。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The worst part of the day was the cockroach that ran across the floor when I turned on the light.",
